ed files. Locally, the repo verifies the presence and wiring of docs files during E2E. The actual rendered Pages build is validated by GitHub Actions."},"515":{"id":"/operate/verification-57","page_id":"/operate/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/operate/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"The CI workflow at `.github/workflows/ci.yml` runs package verification, Docker Compose validation, Helm chart lint/render checks, and the Docker-backed E2E suite. The container workflow at `.github/workflows/container.yml` builds and publishes the ingest image to GitHub Container Registry only after CI succeeds on `main`."},"516":{"id":"/operate/verification-58","page_id":"/operate/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/operate/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Validate deployment artifacts locally with:"},"517":{"id":"/operate/verification-59","page_id":"/operate/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/operate/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Run the local ingest benchmark with:"},"518":{"id":"/operate/verification-60","page_id":"/operate/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/operate/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Package publishability is checked with:"},"519":{"id":"/operate/verification-61","page_id":"/operate/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/operate/verification#when-to-add-e2e-coverage","content":"Add E2E assertions when documentation introduces a new public workflow, API shape, query pattern, or deployment guarantee. Unit tests are enough for internal helpers, but anything shown in `/docs` should either be exercised by `npm run verify:e2e` or explicitly documented as a static/CI-only check."},"520":{"id":"/project/agent-skill","page_id":"/project/agent-skill","type":"page","content":"Coding Agent Skill","breadcrumbs":["Documentation","Project"],"tags":[],"url":"/project/agent-skill"},"521":{"id":"/project/agent-skill-0","page_id":"/project/agent-skill","ta